snippet.textDisplay: Elton John is one of the best selling artists of all time. Ozzy Osbourne is one of the most famous and successful rock stars with both Black Sabbath and solo career along side with him. Yet. It is hard for even these to reach a wider audience with new music. Elton Johns latest music haven't reached nearly as many people in several years and this song has in a few days. Ozzy Osbourne has a bit more "luck" since his name now and again appears in the newspapers, although many times for rather silly things than his actual achievements. Either way. Both artists has done their big share of classic songs and for a later day offering. This isn't so bad!
